title: Woman And Man Holding Hands Medium Dark Skin Tone Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a couple, specifically a woman and a man, holding hands with distinct medium-dark and medium-light skin tones. It signifies a romantic relationship, partnership, or close connection between people of different ethnic backgrounds.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts a couple holding hands, with the woman having a medium-dark skin tone and the man a medium-light skin tone, showcasing Apple’s commitment to diverse representation. Their hands are rendered with realistic lighting and subtle 3D shading, appearing soft and rounded, symbolizing unity and partnership. This visual emphasizes connection and togetherness, a tender gesture of companionship on Apple devices.
